Enum Duration.Value

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Duration.Value>
      • medley.Duration.Value
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Duration.Value>

    Duration

    public static enum Duration.Value
extends Enum<Duration.Value>
    Musical values, that represent the notes durations.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      Breve
      Breve has the time value of two semibreves.
      Crotchet
      Crotchet has the time value of half a Minim or the time value of a quarter of a Semibreve.
      Demisemiquaver
      Demisemiquaver has the time value of half a Semiquaver.
      Hemidemisemiquaver
      Hemidemisemiquaver has the time value of half a Demisemiquaver.
      Minim
      Minim has the time value of half a Semibreve or the time value of two crotchets.
      Quaver
      Quaver has the time value of half a Crotchet or the time value of a quarter of a Minim or the time value of an eighth of a Semibreve.
      Semibreve
      Semibreve has the time value of half a Breve or the time value of two minims or the time value of four crotchets.
      Semiquaver
      Semiquaver has the time value of half a Quaver.
